{
  "text": "To assess the performance of the semi-mechanistic transmission model we compared it to three simpler null models: two representing the constituent parts of the semi-mechanistic model, and a non-mechanistic time series model. For the first null model, we used a deterministic model that only contained the mechanistic core of the semi-mechanistic model, that is a deterministic SEIR model with fixed transmission rate and parameters otherwise the same as in the model described before [CITATION_1] :",
